{"tid":815807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又突破！]公屋輪候期勢破6年！","createTime":"2018-09-12T10:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T07:56:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edf663c3ac84e7c8ca587fd584b21c74278e37cf","tid":815807,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"公屋聯會主席文裕明指，政府建屋量不斷落後於長遠房屋策略目標，<span style=\"color: red;\">公屋輪候時間突破6年可謂「指日可待」</span>，而私人住宅售價指數連續21個月錄得升幅。他批評當局表現「好難畀合格分數」，又指港人現時陷於上樓無期、買樓無力、租樓無奈的「三無」境地。聯會建議政府把公私營房屋比例調高至七三比，並把增建的公營房屋供應量主要撥作興建資助出售房屋，既保留置業元素，亦可透過綠表家庭交回公屋單位，促進房屋流轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180912/bkn-20180912172743281-0912_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180912%2Fbkn-20180912172743281-0912_00822_001.html&d=eglcHZo5bQlIHxwLRU4D2kzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=464efa03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180912/bkn-20180912172743281-0912_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e36def2129f15db03f87978da06d7fea528e7cb3","tid":815807,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b9e630441ec360734e5a997c16273185c02c03","tid":815807,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"上個月定前個月先話破5 咁快就破6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49556ad2842f1dbafb1d51545693d9fab313a44","tid":815807,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"政府：你唔鍾意可以移民去大灣區"},{"pid":"b9e42452d26a64ac56fe1be557cf6c3a69f5437d","tid":815807,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0